\p
\v 9 Te \w dongah|strong="G2532"\w*, \wj “ \+w Yaak|strong="G0191"\+w* nah \+w hna|strong="G3775"\+w* aka \+w khueh|strong="G2192"\+w* \+w loh|strong="G3739"\+w* \+w ya|strong="G0191"\+w* saeh,” \wj* a \w ti|strong="G3004"\w* nah.   
