\v 30 \w Amah|strong="G0846"\w* \w im|strong="G3624"\w* \w la|strong="G1519"\w* a \w caeh|strong="G0565"\w* vaengah \w thingkong|strong="G2825"\w* \w soah|strong="G1909"\w* aka \w yalh|strong="G0906"\w* \w camoe|strong="G3813"\w* \w te|strong="G3588"\w* a \w hmuh|strong="G2147"\w*. Te \w vaengah|strong="G2532"\w* \w rhaithae|strong="G1140"\w* khaw ana \w suntla|strong="G1831"\w* coeng.   
\s1 Hnapang Khaw a Hna Khui  
